  "id": "RAW_828f460d",
  "title": "原 LiblibAI 联创创业获千万美元融资，用“世界模拟器”突围 AI 娱乐",
  "url": "https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=Mzk0MDMyNDUxOQ==&mid=2247497371&idx=1&sn=be251261453ea5010398be00f6404d24",
  "date": "2026-03-10 00:55:00",
  "author": "暗涌Waves",
  "siteName": "暗涌Waves",
  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <p><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-aistatus=\"1\" data-croporisrc=\"https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/sz_mmbiz_png/vicPgQ9MYLWteEKy81uyWXQ8HSYOd564rjDbbHicscArXX6xpz4wL2pcwSEvSg3n1OR93Z02QTFTO4Vuw2U25JEG3EcKuiaY101RVyLwZ40UXg/0?wx_fmt=png&amp;from=appmsg\" data-cropselx2=\"578\" data-cropsely2=\"578\" data-imgfileid=\"100013700\" data-ratio=\"1\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"960\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=a494859a&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FvicPgQ9MYLWteEKy81uyWXQ8HSYOd564rjDbbHicscArXX6xpz4wL2pcwSEvSg3n1OR93Z02QTFTO4Vuw2U25JEG3EcKuiaY101RVyLwZ40UXg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\" style=\"font-size: 1rem; width: 100%;\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-top: 24px;margin-bottom: 48px;text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-size: 20px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 175, 0);\"><strong><span leaf=\"\">「</span></strong></span><span><strong><span leaf=\"\">在自创的虚拟世界，获得一种“奶茶式”的快乐。</span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"text-align: left;font-size: 20px;color: rgb(0, 175, 0);font-weight: bold;\">」</span></strong></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: right;margin-bottom: 0px;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(178, 178, 178);font-size: 12px;\"><span leaf=\"\">文</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 12px;color: rgb(0, 175, 0);\"><span leaf=\"\">｜</span></span><span style=\"font-size:12px;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\">陈之琰</span></strong></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: right;margin-bottom: 0px;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span style=\"font-size:12px;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-aistatus=\"1\" data-backh=\"72\" data-backw=\"578\" data-imgfileid=\"100011910\" data-ratio=\"0.12444444444444444\" data-type=\"gif\" data-w=\"900\" style=\"width: 100%;height: auto !important;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=2d912896&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_gif%2FBhIKFZ2E88gzESQ19UqrtSgjbbIfXapAPVuIicnkFMjZ2m7IPq7oVSPKaK9lLSh3y154FrDKasnyaqiaKd9yF90A%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dgif\"></span></strong></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 24px 16px 0px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;font-size: 14px;font-family: mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;color: rgb(0, 175, 0);letter-spacing: 0.578px;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">「暗涌Waves」独家获悉，</span></span></strong><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;font-size: 14px;font-family: mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;color: rgb(0, 175, 0);letter-spacing: 0.578px;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">AI</span></span></strong><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;font-size: 14px;font-family: mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;color: rgb(0, 175, 0);letter-spacing: 0.578px;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">互动娱乐平台「幕间」已于近期连续完成两轮融资，累计融资金额达千万美元。两轮融资分别由锦秋基金、云九资本领投，包括前网易</span></span></strong><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;font-size: 14px;font-family: mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;color: rgb(0, 175, 0);letter-spacing: 0.578px;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">副总裁</span></span></strong><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;font-size: 14px;font-family: mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;color: rgb(0, 175, 0);letter-spacing: 0.578px;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">少云、原沐瞳</span></span></strong><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;font-size: 14px;font-family: mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;color: rgb(0, 175, 0);letter-spacing: 0.578px;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">CEO</span></span></strong><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;font-size: 14px;font-family: mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;color: rgb(0, 175, 0);letter-spacing: 0.578px;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">袁菁（Justin）在内的</span></span></strong><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;font-size: 14px;font-family: mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;color: rgb(0, 175, 0);letter-spacing: 0.578px;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">多位游戏行业资深人士跟投</span></span></strong><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;font-size: 14px;font-family: mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;color: rgb(0, 175, 0);letter-spacing: 0.578px;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">。</span></span></strong></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 24px 16px 0px;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0.578px;font-family: mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;color: rgb(85, 85, 85);\">我在上海见到了一头红发的「幕间」创始人</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;color: rgb(85, 85, 85);\">Roi</span></span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0.578px;font-family: mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;color: rgb(85, 85, 85);\">，一位以电影《红辣椒》剧照为微信头像的90后女性创业者。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 24px 16px 0px;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;color: rgb(85, 85, 85);\">Roi</span></span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0.578px;font-family: mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;color: rgb(85, 85, 85);\">毕业于北京大学国际政治专业，后赴美于纽约大学攻读交互媒体艺术专业。职业生涯中，她曾任职于乐元素、莉莉丝，担任游戏制作人和主策划，主导过多款国民级产品；随后进入字节跳动教育线，负责游戏化产品设计。</span></span><strong style=\"font-weight: bold;font-size: 14px;font-family: mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;color: rgb(0, 175, 0);letter-spacing: 0.578px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;font-size: 14px;font-family: mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;color: rgb(0, 175, 0);letter-spacing: 0.578px;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">在创办「幕间」之前，</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">Roi</span></span></strong><strong style=\"font-weight: bold;font-size: 14px;font-family: mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;color: rgb(0, 175, 0);letter-spacing: 0.578px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;font-size: 14px;font-family: mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;color: rgb(0, 175, 0);letter-spacing: 0.578px;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">是LiblibAI早期产品负责人。</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0.578px;font-family: mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;color: rgb(85, 85, 85);\">在那里，她亲历了AI工具从0到1的爆发与激烈的算力补贴战，并主导开发了早期的AI自由画布设计工具。随后于2024年离职探索，准备创业。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 24px 16px 0px;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;color: rgb(85, 85, 85);\">Roi</span></span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0.578px;font-family: mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;color: rgb(85, 85, 85);\">告诉「暗涌Waves」，做「幕间」是对AI如何服务于人类娱乐进一步思考后做出的选择。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 24px 16px 0px;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0.578px;font-family: mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;color: rgb(85, 85, 85);\">“和AI聊天久了会乏味，而互动剧、互动小说的选项又太过单调。”她希望打造一个人类与AI新的互动娱乐系统。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 24px 16px 0px;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0.578px;font-family: mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;color: rgb(85, 85, 85);\">作为AI to C创业的重镇，已有几条明显的路径：一种是以CharacterAI、EVE为代表的情感陪伴类产品；一种是深化故事情节的互动小说与互动剧，通过AI生成推动剧情发展，试图打破传统互动玩法的天花板；一种是近期受到关注的Elys，真人与AI分身混杂共存的新一代社交网络。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 24px 16px 0px;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0.578px;font-family: mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;color: rgb(85, 85, 85);\">离开LiblibAI后，</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;color: rgb(85, 85, 85);\">Roi</span></span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0.578px;font-family: mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;color: rgb(85, 85, 85);\">希望通过「幕间」，以一个更具感性色彩与想象力的方式切入人类与AI之间的互动关系：基于UGC的AI模拟器平台。有些类似刚获得1亿美元融资、基于“斯坦福小镇”逻辑的社交沙盒Simile，让用户作为“上帝”观察Agent在系统规则下的自主演化。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 24px 16px 0px;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0.578px;font-family: mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;color: rgb(85, 85, 85);\">在「幕间」内测期间，已经有多个由用户自己创造的模拟器演化出了意想不到的形态——“金主妈妈打赏模拟器”能让使用者用户扮演“榜一”，在虚拟的“抖音直播间”里给几十个AI男主播打赏，看他们如何讨好观众、表演节目；“股票模拟器”将一个名为DeepRich的毒舌大模型引入交易场景，让用户在虚拟的A股市场体验从“清澈大学生”到“金融巨头”的激荡人生；“女明星模拟器”则营造了一个娱乐至上的世界，用户作为顶流女明星参加恋综、处理热搜、粉丝博弈与多角关系。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: right;margin: 24px 16px;line-height: 1em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"text-align: right;line-height: 1em;letter-spacing: 0.578px;font-size: 14px;color: rgb(85, 85, 85);\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-aistatus=\"1\" data-croporisrc=\"https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/sz_mmbiz_gif/vicPgQ9MYLWuibZI0lkxzpKxBiaK4vch0T3J2bicK9hap7cX6gnBkZ1wKxA2XGPWnzoJEPZRyf8GaDOFgmib4MDWWBLrYPSPWMtk9tW1XS498Sc4/0?wx_fmt=gif&amp;from=appmsg\" data-cropselx2=\"546\" data-cropsely2=\"383\" data-imgfileid=\"100013715\" data-ratio=\"0.7490247074122237\" data-type=\"gif\" data-w=\"769\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=c630dba0&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_gif%2FvicPgQ9MYLWuibZI0lkxzpKxBiaK4vch0T3J2bicK9hap7cX6gnBkZ1wKxA2XGPWnzoJEPZRyf8GaDOFgmib4MDWWBLrYPSPWMtk9tW1XS498Sc4%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dgif%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"text-align: right;line-height: 1em;letter-spacing: 0.578px;font-size: 12px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">模拟器展示页面｜图片来源：企业供图</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 24px 16px 0px;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0.578px;font-family: mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;color: rgb(85, 85, 85);\">用一种更好理解的方式来解释「幕间」到底是什么，可以说，</span></span><strong style=\"font-weight: bold;font-size: 14px;font-family: mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;color: rgb(0, 175, 0);letter-spacing: 0.578px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;font-size: 14px;font-family: mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;color: rgb(0, 175, 0);letter-spacing: 0.578px;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">它并非传统意义上的游戏，更像是一个集成密室、剧本杀、短剧、游戏的线上综合游乐园。平台上的创作者通过使用提供的</span></span></strong><strong style=\"font-weight: bold;font-size: 14px;font-family: mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;color: rgb(0, 175, 0);letter-spacing: 0.578px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;font-size: 14px;font-family: mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;color: rgb(0, 175, 0);letter-spacing: 0.578px;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">AI</span></span></strong><strong style=\"font-weight: bold;font-size: 14px;font-family: mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;color: rgb(0, 175, 0);letter-spacing: 0.578px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;font-size: 14px;font-family: mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;color: rgb(0, 175, 0);letter-spacing: 0.578px;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">制作工具创造不同的世界，用户通过平台选择、进入、并沉浸其中。</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0.578px;font-family: mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;color: rgb(85, 85, 85);\">较传统游戏来说，「幕间」更轻量、更碎片，也更强调完全个性化的反馈。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 24px 16px 0px;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;color: rgb(85, 85, 85);\">Roi</span></span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0.578px;font-family: mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;color: rgb(85, 85, 85);\">告诉「暗涌Waves」，「幕间」不是米其林，而希望提供一种类似“奶茶式”的快乐——它不像3A大作那样精美绝伦，但足够好喝、爽口、过瘾，且能持续提供专属的情绪价值。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: right;margin: 40px 16px 8px;line-height: 1.6em;\" data-pm-slice=\"4 4 []\"><span style=\"font-size:24px;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\">Part</span></strong></span><span style=\"font-size: 24px;color: rgb(0, 175, 0);\"><strong><span leaf=\"\">01</span></strong></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: right;margin: 0px 16px;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 24px;color: rgb(0, 175, 0);\"><strong><span leaf=\"\">野生实验</span></strong></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 24px 16px 0px;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0.578px;font-family: mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;color: rgb(85, 85, 85);\">在</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;color: rgb(85, 85, 85);\">Roi</span></span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0.578px;font-family: mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;color: rgb(85, 85, 85);\">的逻辑里，「幕间」不仅仅是一个消费内容的地方，它更像是一个让“野生”创意自由生长的实验室。不同于传统游戏工业那套层级森严、动辄数亿元投入的管线，在这里，内容的生命力来自于一群原本与代码毫无关系的年轻人。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 24px 16px 0px;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0.578px;font-family: mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;color: rgb(85, 85, 85);\">在开始创业的这段时间，最出乎</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;color: rgb(85, 85, 85);\">Roi</span></span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0.578px;font-family: mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;color: rgb(85, 85, 85);\">意料的是，平台很快凝聚起来的、最核心的一批创作者并非专业游戏从业者或程序员，竟然多是来自一二线城市的“00后”女生。这些创作者也是玩家，最初的驱动力极度纯粹——为了在虚拟世界里“捏”出一个完美的理想型，并和TA谈一场永不落幕的恋爱。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 24px 16px 0px;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0.578px;font-family: mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;color: rgb(85, 85, 85);\">这种强烈的表达欲让她们跨越了技术的鸿沟。通过自学AI编程，这些此前和“技术”毫不沾边的女孩，正拿着手机在宿舍里、在工作间隙“手搓”出界面精美、逻辑复杂的模拟器。她们研究提示词工程、调优语料、设计互动逻辑。这种基于AI时代原生的Vibe Coding方式，让游戏圈的“老炮”少云、袁菁（Justin）都感到惊讶，进而几乎没有犹豫，直接投资了「幕间」。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 24px 16px 0px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;font-size: 14px;font-family: mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;color: rgb(0, 175, 0);letter-spacing: 0.578px;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">为了能够凝聚这群创作动力蓬勃的核心资产，「幕间」为这些创作者提供了一整套工具</span></span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;font-size: 14px;font-family: mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;color: rgb(0, 175, 0);letter-spacing: 0.578px;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">链，使其能像搭</span></span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;font-size: 14px;font-family: mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;color: rgb(0, 175, 0);letter-spacing: 0.578px;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">建乐高积木一样搭建agent：</span></span></strong></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin: 24px 16px 0px;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0.578px;font-family: mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;color: rgb(85, 85, 85);\">用户可以基</span></span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0.578px;font-family: mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;color: rgb(85, 85, 85);\">于</span></span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0.578px;font-family: mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;color: rgb(85, 85, 85);\">Producer Agent，通过组合导演、玩法、交互等多</span></span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0.578px;font-family: mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;color: rgb(85, 85, 85);\">种</span></span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0.578px;font-family: mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, 