mily: mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;color: rgb(85, 85, 85);\">LUI、Cloud Identit</span></span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0.578px;font-family: mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;color: rgb(85, 85, 85);\">y</span></span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0.578px;font-family: mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;color: rgb(85, 85, 85);\">等工具，</span></span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0.578px;font-family: mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;color: rgb(85, 85, 85);\">让</span></span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0.578px;font-family: mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;color: rgb(85, 85, 85);\">Agen</span></span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0.578px;font-family: mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;color: rgb(85, 85, 85);\">t</span></span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0.578px;font-family: mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;color: rgb(85, 85, 85);\">可以创造出惊艳的多模态体验和易用的交互方式。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: right;margin: 24px 16px 0px;line-height: 1em;\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-aistatus=\"1\" data-height=\"1387\" data-imgfileid=\"100013706\" data-ratio=\"0.5416666666666666\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-width=\"2560\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=5148ce97&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FvicPgQ9MYLWtQ0EARoEBdMuzda6VRbPlHJGJJMAeECdsKCJr952EBkicgFuypgI1UgVg2dxudEianID6G3jryJfALicxWcGHiaiaFYjmY3m0VplNE%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: right;margin: 0px 16px;line-height: 1em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"text-align: right;line-height: 1em;letter-spacing: 0.578px;font-size: 12px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;p&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;text-align: right; margin: 24px 16px 0px; line-height: 1em;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\">工具栏展示页面｜图片来源：企业供图</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 24px 16px 0px;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0.578px;font-family: mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;color: rgb(85, 85, 85);\">此外，</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;color: rgb(85, 85, 85);\">Roi</span></span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0.578px;font-family: mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;color: rgb(85, 85, 85);\">还采取了一种“社区驱动”的打法。她招募了一批具备“爱好者”特点运营团队，对核心创作者进行“一对一”的“贴身服务”。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 24px 16px 0px;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;color: rgb(85, 85, 85);\">Roi</span></span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0.578px;font-family: mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;color: rgb(85, 85, 85);\">告诉「暗涌Waves」，这种深度服务一方面是增强产品粘性，更是在了解创作者和用户需求的同时，强化为用户创作的能力。「幕间」还通过定期开课、布置作业、强行在社区内进行作品PK与反馈循环。显然，这个创业团队正试图在AI时代复刻B站早期的社区共鸣——让第一批最硬核的玩家成为创作者，进而在生态内循环的基础上，逐步出圈。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: right;margin: 40px 16px 8px;line-height: 1.6em;\" data-pm-slice=\"4 4 []\"><span style=\"font-size:24px;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\">Part</span></strong></span><span style=\"font-size: 24px;color: rgb(0, 175, 0);\"><strong><span leaf=\"\">02</span></strong></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: right;margin: 0px 16px;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 24px;color: rgb(0, 175, 0);\"><strong><span leaf=\"\">不一样的“情绪生意”</span></strong></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 24px 16px 0px;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0.578px;font-family: mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;color: rgb(85, 85, 85);\">当谈及「幕间」的商业想象力时，</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;color: rgb(85, 85, 85);\">Roi</span></span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0.578px;font-family: mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;color: rgb(85, 85, 85);\">认为要赚的是“溢价”与“基建”的钱。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 24px 16px 0px;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0.578px;font-family: mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;color: rgb(85, 85, 85);\">一方面，作为平台方，在底层Token的规模化供给上赚取合理的利差，并从优秀作品的收益中进行抽成。另一方面，随着低成本模型能力的提升，一些互动成本极低的模拟器（如轻量级的策略小游戏）甚至有机会跑通广告模式。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 24px 16px 0px;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0.578px;font-family: mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;color: rgb(85, 85, 85);\">在</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;color: rgb(85, 85, 85);\">Roi</span></span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0.578px;font-family: mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;color: rgb(85, 85, 85);\">看来，相比于传统游戏巨头和AI大厂，「幕间」有两条护城河：</span></span><strong style=\"font-weight: bold;font-size: 14px;font-family: mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;color: rgb(0, 175, 0);letter-spacing: 0.578px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;font-size: 14px;font-family: mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;color: rgb(0, 175, 0);letter-spacing: 0.578px;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">首先是极低的内容生产成本与高频试错率。</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0.578px;font-family: mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;color: rgb(85, 85, 85);\">传统游戏做一个角色可能要投入500万人民币，而「幕间」上的创作者利用AI只需要一周就能上线一个模拟器。这种极高的内容密度，能够覆盖无数传统工业无法触达的长尾需求。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 24px 16px 0px;line-height: 1.6em;\"><strong style=\"font-weight: bold;font-size: 14px;font-family: mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;color: rgb(0, 175, 0);letter-spacing: 0.578px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;font-size: 14px;font-family: mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;color: rgb(0, 175, 0);letter-spacing: 0.578px;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">其次则是原生开发者的独占性。</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;color: rgb(85, 85, 85);\">Roi</span></span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0.578px;font-family: mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;color: rgb(85, 85, 85);\">认为，正如《蛋仔派对》的头部开发者并非来自《Minecraft》，AI时代的原生开发者也不会来自传统游戏公司。“在「幕间」体系内成长起来创作者将很快习惯这套工具与社群语境，这种先发优势很难被模仿。”</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 24px 16px 0px;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;color: rgb(85, 85, 85);\">Roi</span></span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0.578px;font-family: mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;color: rgb(85, 85, 85);\">和「幕间」的野心显然不止于恋爱模拟。</span></span><strong style=\"font-weight: bold;font-size: 14px;font-family: mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;color: rgb(0, 175, 0);letter-spacing: 0.578px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;font-size: 14px;font-family: mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;color: rgb(0, 175, 0);letter-spacing: 0.578px;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">即将到来的3月中下旬，「幕间」计</span></span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"line-height: 1.6em;font-weight: bold;font-size: 14px;font-family: mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;color: rgb(0, 175, 0);letter-spacing: 0.578px;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">划开启更大规模的测试和模拟器开发大赛，世界</span></span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;font-size: 14px;font-family: mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;color: rgb(0, 175, 0);letter-spacing: 0.578px;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">模拟器的“品类”也将拓宽至修仙、职场、历史演化等更广泛的领域。</span></span></strong></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 24px 16px 0px;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0.578px;font-family: mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;color: rgb(85, 85, 85);\">问题是，UGC的世界模拟器能够与成熟游戏厂商和3A大作抗衡吗？</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 24px 16px 0px;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0.578px;font-family: mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;color: rgb(85, 85, 85);\">对此，</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;color: rgb(85, 85, 85);\">Roi</span></span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0.578px;font-family: mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;color: rgb(85, 85, 85);\">引用了米哈游创始人蔡浩宇的观点，“未来游戏创造将只属于两类人，顶尖的天才团队和业余爱好者。其中0.0001%的顶尖人才将组成精英团队，创造出前所未有的游戏作品；而99%的业余爱好者则可以根据自己的兴趣随意创造游戏。”</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 24px 16px 0px;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;color: rgb(85, 85, 85);\">Roi</span></span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0.578px;font-family: mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;color: rgb(85, 85, 85);\">说：“在那片海量的99%中，我想造出一个不可撼动的超级游乐场。”</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 32px 16px 0px;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0.578px;font-size: 12px;color: rgb(178, 178, 178);\"><span leaf=\"\">排版｜姚楠</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 16px 16px;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0.578px;font-size: 12px;color: rgb(178, 178, 178);\"><span style=\"color: rgb(178, 178, 178);font-size: 12px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;\"><span leaf=\"\">图片来源｜IC Photo</span></span></span></p>\n </body>\n</html>",
  "aiSummary": "原 LiblibAI 联创 Roi 创办的 AI 互动娱乐平台「幕间」获千万美元融资，主打基于 UGC 的“世界模拟器”，通过轻量化、高情感价值的 AI 互动体验突围 AI 娱乐赛道。",
  "oneSentenceSummary": "原 LiblibAI 联创 Roi 创办的 AI 互动娱乐平台「幕间」获千万美元融资，主打基于 UGC 的“世界模拟器”，通过轻量化、高情感价值的 AI 互动体验突围 AI 娱乐赛道。",
  "summary": "本文报道了 AI 创业公司「幕间」的融资进展及其核心产品逻辑。创始人 Roi（原 LiblibAI 产品负责人）认为当前的 AI 聊天和互动剧过于单调，因此提出“世界模拟器”概念，打造一个基于 UGC 的 AI 社交沙盒。该平台允许用户利用 AI 工具（Vibe Coding）低门槛地创造如“金主妈妈模拟器”、“女明星模拟器”等具有高度个性化反馈和情绪价值的模拟器。文章强调，其核心创作者并非专业程序员，而是极具表达欲的 00 后女性群体。通过极低的内容生产成本和社区驱动的运营模式，「幕间」试图在 3A 大作之外，为用户提供“奶茶式”的碎片化快乐，并构建 AI 时代原生的开发者生态。",
  "mainPoints": [
    {
      "point": "从单一的情感陪伴转向复杂的“世界模拟器”系统。",
      "explanation": "不同于 CharacterAI 的线性聊天，幕间通过 Agent 演化逻辑，让用户在特定规则的模拟器中体验多角关系、社会博弈等更具深度的互动。"
    },
    {
      "point": "AI 降低了创作门槛，催生了非专业背景的“原生开发者”。",
      "explanation": "核心创作者多为 00 后女性，她们通过“手搓”提示词和 AI 工具实现复杂的互动逻辑，这种 Vibe Coding 模式打破了传统游戏开发的工业管线。"
    },
    {
      "point": "追求“奶茶式”的快乐，聚焦长尾的情绪价值需求。",
      "explanation": "产品定位并非追求 3A 大作的精美，而是通过极低成本、高频迭代的内容，覆盖传统游戏工业无法触达的碎片化、个性化情感需求。"
    },
    {
      "point": "构建基于 AI 原生工具链的社区护城河。",
      "explanation": "通过提供 Producer Agent、多模态渲染等工具链，并配合深度社区服务，吸引并留住第一批硬核创作者，形成难以模仿的生态先发优势。"
    }
  ],
  "keyQuotes": [
    "在自创的虚拟世界，获得一种'奶茶式'的快乐。",
    "和 AI 聊天久了会乏味，而互动剧、互动小说的选项又太过单调。",
    "它并非传统意义上的游戏，更像是一个集成密室、剧本杀、短剧、游戏的线上综合游乐园。",
    "未来游戏创造将只属于两类人，顶尖的天才团队和业余爱好者。",
    "在那片海量的 99%中，我想造出一个不可撼动的超级游乐场。"
  ],
